{"tid":2143188,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國趕絕中概股，不符合審計要求或於2022年１月強行除牌","createTime":"2020-08-07T03:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T12:04:40.000Z","uid":48040,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"31bc3320ea0af125dfe069795d84c09ed89b04c2","tid":2143188,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T03:04:56.000Z","msg":"美國財政部及證券交易委員會(SEC)官員向特朗普總統提出建議，在2022年1月前，將在美國上市但不符合美國法律審計要求的中國企業全部摘牌。<br />\n<br />\n據路透社周四的報道指，特朗普早前委任財政部長姆努欽（Steven Mnuchin）與證券交易委員會主席克萊頓(Jay Clayton)等高級官員參與工作小組，評估如何處置在美國上市但審計不符合要求的中國企業，並且為此撰寫報告。<br />\n<br />\n財政部官員周四就上述報告進度向路透社表示，小組將建議特朗普，要求美國上市的中國企業必須在2022年1月前，符合其他美國上市公司所達到的審計要求，即容許相應的監管機構，美國公眾公司會計監督委員會 (PCAOB)取得它們的審計報告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://rfi.my/6LOr.T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frfi.my%2F6LOr.T&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLHobfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=af74eca6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rfi.my/6LOr.T</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1291570302929874944?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1291570302929874944%3Fs%3D20&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLHobfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=e326008c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1291570302929874944%3Fs%3D20&h=b26b91a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1291570302929874944?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"32e2f6e10c632e8ead40f32acfb3e1bc675f578e","tid":2143188,"uid":55089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T03:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92179bb5484220dd4cf5c4f3d81d1e884ef1f20b","tid":2143188,"uid":156327,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"repl